# 🐱 IDEA 2 — MEOWDORO GROUP (Accountability Pool)

## PROJECT NAME

Meowdoro Group

## PROBLEM (1 sentence)

A group of 4 college students in Manila planning to study together online fail to stay consistent, leading to missed deadlines and wasted shared study sessions.

## SOLUTION (1 sentence)

Each member deposits USDC into a shared pool, and a Soroban contract redistributes rewards only to members who complete sessions—using Stellar for transparent, instant settlement.

## STELLAR FEATURES USED

* USDC transfers
* Soroban smart contracts
* Trustlines

## TARGET USERS

* Study groups / barkadas
* Philippines / SEA
* Motivated by peer pressure + money incentives

## CORE FEATURE (MVP)

4 users deposit 5 USDC → contract records participants → only those who mark completion receive equal split of total pool

## WHY THIS WINS

Social + financial coordination = strong use case; demonstrates **multi-user contract logic + real fund redistribution** (very hackathon-friendly).

## OPTIONAL EDGE

Offline timer sync + QR-based join system

